<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-business-innovation-skills> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Department for Business, Innovation and Skills (BIS) and the Department of Energy and Climate Change (DECC) have merged to form the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (BEIS). For information on education and skills, see the Department for Education (DfE) . For information on trade, see the Department for International Trade (DIT) ."@en .
